Serialized Form

  • Package org.mkosciesza.ocilib

    • Class org.mkosciesza.ocilib.CallUpdateEvent extends CapEvent implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • personality

          int personality
          The personality of the call. The personality indicates whether this user originated this call or this call was placed to the user.

          Possible values:

          0 - BroadWorks Originator

          1 - Originator

          2 - Terminator

        • state

          int state
          The state of the call.

          Possible values:

          0 - idle

          1 - alerting

          2 - active

          3 - held

          4 - remote held

          5 - released

          6 - detached

          7 - client alerting

        • releaseCause

          int releaseCause
          The release cause of the call. This tag has meaning when the call is released. Until then, it has a default value of “0” that can be ignored.

        • remoteNumber

          java.lang.String remoteNumber
          The remote phone number in the call.

        • remoteName

          java.lang.String remoteName
          The remote name (if available) in the call.

        • callType

          int callType
          The call type for this call leg.

          0 - unknown

          1 - intra-group

          2 - enterprise

          3 - network

          4 - network URL

          5 - emergency

          6 - repair

          7 - error

          8 - city-wide centrex

          9 - private dial plan

          2 - CAP registration failed

          Short description of the cause of connection failure.
